In this set of chapters, further steps were taken to reduce Brent's constraints. Additionally, Patty created a kanban board with which to monitor flow of individual task processes and placed emphasis on the IT self-improvement cycle. A phoenix task that was assigned to Brent highlighted another production plant-related issue in IT. Hand-offs are something that can be lost in a lot of issue tracking systems, especially when those hand-offs are between people in different teams.
